snippet.title: 3D Watermelon Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to play the most delicious game yet! 3D Watermelon is now on Steam and this trailer will give you a sneak peek of what's to come. Score your way through this puzzle game and be the first to reach the top of the leaderboard. Are you ready to take on the challenge? Download 3D Watermelon on Steam now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2707420/3D_Watermelon_Game/
